    <item>
      <title>在巴基斯坦谈判中，伊朗看到美国试图发号施令，而不是谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/middleeast/iran-united-states-negotiations.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗认为美国的要求远远超出了其在战争中取得的成就。专家表示，德黑兰赌的是自己能够承受进一步的轰炸，而华盛顿却不愿意维持经济混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/middleeast/iran-united-states-negotiations.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 11:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
